---
---

<section id="schedule" class="py-20 bg-cream">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="font-display italic text-gold text-lg mb-2">The week ahead</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-wine">Schedule</h2>
      <p class="ornament text-gold/50 text-sm mt-4">&mdash; &#10049; &mdash;</p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-charcoal/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Four gatherings that bring us all together, and three leisurely days
        to explore Burgundy at your own pace. Every evening, the estate is yours.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">

      <!-- ═══════ JULY 4 — ORGANISED ═══════ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden border-l-4 border-gold">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-800 via-red-700 to-blue-800 p-6 text-white">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <p class="text-white/70 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Saturday, July 4</p>
              <h3 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold">The 250th Independence Day</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-white/20 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Arrival &middot; Organised</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Daytime</h4>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70">
                Arrivals and settling in. Explore the estate, take a dip in the pool,
                and get to know the space. Drinks and snacks will be waiting.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Evening</h4>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-3">
                <strong>BBQ &amp; themed party.</strong> Dress code: red, white &amp; blue.
                American-themed food and cocktails on the terrace. Sparklers for the children.
              </p>
              <a href="https://open.spotify.com/playlist/YOUR_PLAYLIST_ID" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
                 class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-green-700 font-medium hover:text-green-800">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 0C5.4 0 0 5.4 0 12s5.4 12 12 12 12-5.4 12-12S18.66 0 12 0zm5.521 17.34c-.24.359-.66.48-1.021.24-2.82-1.74-6.36-2.101-10.561-1.141-.418.122-.779-.179-.899-.539-.12-.421.18-.78.54-.9 4.56-1.021 8.52-.6 11.64 1.32.42.18.479.659.301 1.02zm1.44-3.3c-.301.42-.841.6-1.262.3-3.239-1.98-8.159-2.58-11.939-1.38-.479.12-1.02-.12-1.14-.6-.12-.48.12-1.021.6-1.141C9.6 9.9 15 10.561 18.72 12.84c.361.181.54.78.241 1.2zm.12-3.36C15.24 8.4 8.82 8.16 5.16 9.301c-.6.179-1.2-.181-1.38-.721-.18-.601.18-1.2.72-1.381 4.26-1.26 11.28-1.02 15.721 1.621.539.3.719 1.02.419 1.56-.299.421-1.02.599-1.559.3z"/></svg>
                Contribute to the July 4th Playlist
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ═══════ JULY 5 — LEISURE ═══════ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden border-l-4 border-cream-dark">
        <div class="bg-cream-dark p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <p class="text-charcoal/50 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Sunday, July 5</p>
              <h3 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal">Leisure Day &mdash; <em>Wine &amp; Heritage</em></h3>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-charcoal/10 text-charcoal/60 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">At your leisure</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
          <p class="text-charcoal/60 italic mb-6">
            A day to settle in and explore at your own rhythm. Here are some ideas &mdash;
            organise amongst yourselves or simply enjoy the pool.
          </p>
          <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-4">Suggested Activities</h4>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
            <a href="https://www.chateaudecouches.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Ch&acirc;teau de Couches</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">11th-century castle, wine tasting (6 wines), underground passages. Kids love the tunnels. 25 min drive. &euro;14/&euro;4.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.vins-laly.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Cave Laly, Autun</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">1,500 Burgundy wine references. Stock up for the week. 20 min drive.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.autun-tourisme.com/decouvrez/instant-gourmand-specialites-bourguignonnes/la-route-des-vins-et-le-couchois/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Route des Vins du Couchois</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">Self-drive wine route through villages and small producers. A beautiful afternoon drive.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Dinner Suggestions</h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm mb-3">Eat at the estate or try one of these (book on your own):</p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3">
              <a href="http://lechateaubriant.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-3 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal text-sm">Le Ch&acirc;teaubriant</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/50">Autun &middot; 20 min</p>
              </a>
              <a href="https://labrasseriedeshalles.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-3 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal text-sm">Brasserie des Halles</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/50">Nolay &middot; 30 min</p>
              </a>
              <a href="https://fr.restaurantguru.com/Au-Tire-Bouchon-Nolay" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-3 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal text-sm">Au Tire Bouchon</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/50">Nolay &middot; 30 min</p>
              </a>
              <a href="https://pizza-leo-71.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-3 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal text-sm">Pizza L&eacute;o</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/50">Epinac &middot; Takeaway</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ═══════ JULY 6 — ORGANISED: CYCLING TO AUTUN ═══════ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden border-l-4 border-gold">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-sage to-sage-light p-6 text-white">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <p class="text-white/70 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Monday, July 6</p>
              <h3 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold">Cycling Expedition to Autun</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-white/20 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Organised</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">The Ride</h4>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-3">
                A group cycle along the <strong>Voie Verte</strong> &mdash; a flat, scenic path
                on a former railway that runs from Epinac all the way to Autun (13&nbsp;km).
                Perfect for families, with bikes for all ages including child seats and e-bikes
                from <strong>Morvan Bike Autun</strong>.
              </p>
              <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm italic">
                Please indicate your interest on the travel form so we can arrange bike numbers.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Discovering Autun</h4>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-3">
                Once we reach Autun, two thousand years of history unfold:
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-charcoal/70 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-gold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
                  <span><strong>Roman Theatre</strong> &mdash; one of the largest in ancient Gaul, free entry</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-gold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
                  <span><strong>Temple of Janus</strong> &mdash; a Gallo-Roman temple ruin in open fields</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-gold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
                  <span><strong>Cath&eacute;drale Saint-Lazare</strong> &mdash; 12th-century masterpiece with remarkable Romanesque tympanum</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-gold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
                  <span><strong>Porte d&rsquo;Arroux</strong> &amp; <strong>Porte Saint-Andr&eacute;</strong> &mdash; Roman gates still standing</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm text-charcoal/60">
            <span><strong>Bikes:</strong> Morvan Bike Autun &middot; 09 54 10 21 04</span>
            <span class="text-gold">|</span>
            <span><strong>Route:</strong> Flat &middot; 13 km each way &middot; All ages</span>
            <span class="text-gold">|</span>
            <span><strong>Lunch:</strong> Restaurants in Autun or packed picnic</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ═══════ JULY 7 — ORGANISED: LAKE DAY ═══════ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden border-l-4 border-gold">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-500 p-6 text-white">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <p class="text-white/70 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Tuesday, July 7</p>
              <h3 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold">Lake Day at Lac des Settons</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-white/20 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Organised</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-6">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">On the Water</h4>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-3">
                A full day at <strong>Lac des Settons</strong> &mdash; a stunning 366-hectare lake
                in the heart of the Morvan Natural Park (~1h15 drive).
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-charcoal/70 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-gold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
                  <span>Sailing school, kayak, paddleboard &amp; pedalo (Settons Nautisme)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-gold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
                  <span>Inflatable water park on the lake &mdash; children adore it</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-gold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
                  <span>Supervised swimming at Plage du Midi (Blue Flag beach)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <span class="text-gold mt-0.5">&#8250;</span>
                  <span>Picnic on the shore or lakeside restaurant</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
              <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm italic mt-3">
                Please indicate your interest on the travel form so we can coordinate transport.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Evening &mdash; Pizza Night</h4>
              <p class="text-charcoal/70 mb-4">
                After a day on the water, dinner is easy: pizza night back at the estate.
              </p>
              <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-4">
                <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Pizza L&eacute;o</h5>
                <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60 mt-1">
                  Artisan pizzas &amp; burgers, right here in Epinac.<br/>
                  40+ varieties &middot; &euro;9&ndash;14.50 &middot; Food truck available.
                </p>
                <p class="text-sm text-gold-dark mt-2 font-medium">07 61 02 52 54</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ═══════ JULY 8 — LEISURE ═══════ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden border-l-4 border-cream-dark">
        <div class="bg-cream-dark p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <p class="text-charcoal/50 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Wednesday, July 8</p>
              <h3 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal">Leisure Day &mdash; <em>Nature &amp; Adventure</em></h3>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-charcoal/10 text-charcoal/60 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">At your leisure</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
          <p class="text-charcoal/60 italic mb-6">
            For the adventurous spirits &mdash; treetops, ancient ruins, or the open trail.
            These are suggestions; make your own plans with whoever fancies the same thing.
          </p>
          <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-4">Suggested Activities</h4>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
            <a href="https://acrogivry.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Acrogivry &mdash; Treetop Adventure</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">Burgundy&rsquo;s largest adventure park. 31 courses, 350+ challenges. Kids from age 3. ~40 min. &euro;14&ndash;24.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.bibracte.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Bibracte</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">Ancient Gaulish capital on Mont Beuvray. Museum + archaeological site. ~45 min drive.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.lesgambades-equitation.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Pony &amp; Horse Riding</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">Les Gambades &mdash; baby pony from age 4, trail rides in the Morvan. &euro;19/h.</p>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Dinner Suggestions</h4>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
              <a href="http://lechateaubriant.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-3 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal text-sm">Le Ch&acirc;teaubriant</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/50">Autun &middot; 20 min</p>
              </a>
              <a href="https://labrasseriedeshalles.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-3 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal text-sm">Brasserie des Halles</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/50">Nolay &middot; 30 min</p>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.autun-tourisme.com/offres/a-lheure-des-saveurs-couches-fr-4999013/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-3 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
                <p class="font-semibold text-charcoal text-sm">A l&rsquo;Heure des Saveurs</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-charcoal/50">Couches &middot; 25 min</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ═══════ JULY 9 — LEISURE ═══════ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden border-l-4 border-cream-dark">
        <div class="bg-cream-dark p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <p class="text-charcoal/50 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Thursday, July 9</p>
              <h3 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal">Leisure Day &mdash; <em>Rest &amp; Wander</em></h3>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-charcoal/10 text-charcoal/60 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm">At your leisure</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
          <p class="text-charcoal/60 italic mb-6">
            The day before the party. Take it easy, or slip away for one last adventure.
          </p>
          <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-4">Suggested Activities</h4>
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-5">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Pool &amp; Grounds</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">Heated pool, terraces, game room. Nowhere to be, nothing to do but enjoy.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://www.beaune-tourisme.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Beaune Day Trip</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">The wine capital of Burgundy (40 min). Hosp&iacute;ces, wine cellars, and the charming old town.</p>
            </a>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-5">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">V&eacute;lorail du Morvan</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">Family pedal-carts on old railway tracks through the countryside. ~45 min drive.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://www.autun-tourisme.com/evadez-vous/en-famille/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Raptor Walk</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">&Eacute;chapp&eacute;e Morvan d&rsquo;Ailes &mdash; walk with birds of prey. Magical for children.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://www.autun-tourisme.com/offres/balade-contee-le-temps-des-mines-epinac-fr-3701961/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="block bg-cream rounded-xl p-5 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Mining Heritage Walk</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">Circuit des Gueules Noires (9.5 km, from Epinac). Discover the town&rsquo;s industrial past.</p>
            </a>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-5">
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal mb-1">Base de Loisirs de la Dr&eacute;e</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-charcoal/60">Mini-golf, playground, ping-pong by the river. In Epinac, free entry.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Evening &mdash; Pre-Party</h4>
            <p class="text-charcoal/70">
              Cocktails by the pool, early night in. Tomorrow is the big day.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ═══════ JULY 10 — ORGANISED: THE ANNIVERSARY ═══════ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden border-l-4 border-gold">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-dark via-gold to-gold-light p-6 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 width=%2220%22 height=%2220%22><circle cx=%2210%22 cy=%2210%22 r=%221.5%22 fill=%22white%22/></svg>'); background-size: 20px 20px;"></div>
          <div class="relative flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <p class="text-white/80 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Friday, July 10</p>
              <h3 class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold">The Anniversary</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-white/20 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Organised</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">Day</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-charcoal/70">
                <li><strong>Morning:</strong> Relaxed brunch at the estate</li>
                <li><strong>Afternoon:</strong> Free time &mdash; pool, relax, children with the babysitter</li>
                <li><strong>Late afternoon:</strong> Time to get dressed up</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-display font-semibold text-wine mb-3">The Party</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-charcoal/70">
                <li>&#10042; <strong>Ap&eacute;ritif</strong> on the terrace at sunset</li>
                <li>&#10042; <strong>Catered dinner</strong> under the stars</li>
                <li>&#10042; <strong>Music &amp; dancing</strong> until late</li>
                <li>&#10042; <strong>Children&rsquo;s corner</strong> with babysitter, films &amp; games</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-8 bg-gold/10 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="font-display text-xl text-wine italic">
              &ldquo;The best thing to hold onto in life is each other.&rdquo;
            </p>
            <p class="text-charcoal/50 text-sm mt-2">&mdash; Audrey Hepburn</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ═══════ JULY 11 — DEPARTURE ═══════ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-charcoal to-charcoal/80 p-6 text-white">
          <p class="text-white/70 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Saturday, July 11</p>
